1
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry... I... I...</font>

2
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:11,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I put the secret elixir of the sea 
in Prince Aquasteed's tea!</font>

3
00:00:11,930 --> 00:00:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't cry, Icilla.</font>

4
00:00:16,630 --> 00:00:20,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stop! Look at me!</i></font>

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aqua!</i></font>

6
00:00:35,720 --> 00:00:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an2}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="28"><b><font color="#f76bb3">The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
<font color="#6b3e34">by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

7
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font color="#6b3e34"><font size="25">My <b><font color="#f76bb3">Beautiful <font color="#3d8afc">Lady</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

8
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aqua?</i></font>

9
00:02:13,010 --> 00:02:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed.</font>

10
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:20,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything is ready. 
We must hurry to the ocean.</font>

11
00:02:33,230 --> 00:02:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't believe I spoke 
to Tiara in that voice.</i></font>

12
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Tiara, you can wait here 
at the castle if you want.</font>

13
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:49,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the worst man alive!</font>

14
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can say that again!</font>

15
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:55,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So how is that love potion 
actually affecting you?</font>

16
00:02:55,990 --> 00:02:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's calmed down compared to before,</font>

17
00:02:58,450 --> 00:03:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm still in trouble 
if I see Lady Icilla.</font>

18
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My heart is wavering.</i></font>

19
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I love Tiara so much...</i></font>

20
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to say the name of the one I love,</i></font>

21
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I feel like another name 
will slip out.</i></font>

22
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just what is love, anyway?</font>

23
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the only one who's all alone.</font>

24
00:04:56,620 --> 00:05:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. How long has it been 
since it was this bad?</font>

25
00:05:00,570 --> 00:05:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About 700 years.</font>

26
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you gonna do?</font>

27
00:05:04,990 --> 00:05:08,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're basically the entire 
cause of it this time.</font>

28
00:05:09,890 --> 00:05:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dislike the woman called Tiararose.</font>

29
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She has some nerve leading Claire on.</font>

30
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Pearl said that 
Lady Tiararose is leading you on.</font>

31
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If Pearl really did say that,</i></font>

32
00:05:23,610 --> 00:05:26,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>maybe I can hold 
on to the tiniest shred of hope.</i></font>

33
00:05:27,130 --> 00:05:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Though I can't just come out 
and ask, "You were jealous?"</i></font>

34
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Keith.</font>

35
00:05:34,090 --> 00:05:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just had a great idea. 
Would you help me with it?</font>

36
00:05:36,740 --> 00:05:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

37
00:05:37,890 --> 00:05:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your problem. 
Why do I have to clean up after you?</font>

38
00:05:46,020 --> 00:05:47,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. Just this once.</font>

39
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had a feeling you'd say that.</font>

40
00:05:50,830 --> 00:05:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, really? So what do you want me to do?</font>

41
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're moving too quickly! 
Let's rest for a bit!</font>

42
00:06:08,350 --> 00:06:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine!</font>

43
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed!</font>

44
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:22,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this an effect of the drug?</i></font>

45
00:06:22,870 --> 00:06:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know in my head 
that it's inconceivable,</i></font>

46
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but my body thirsts for Lady Icilla.</i></font>

47
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's return to the castle for now. 
In that condition, you can't...</font>

48
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

49
00:06:34,820 --> 00:06:37,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to get to the ocean, 
whatever it takes.</font>

50
00:06:38,710 --> 00:06:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed...</font>

51
00:06:46,350 --> 00:06:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua!</font>

52
00:06:50,850 --> 00:06:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara?</font>

53
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it's me.</font>

54
00:06:54,890 --> 00:06:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

55
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

56
00:07:01,570 --> 00:07:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. It's because of the love potion.</i></font>

57
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not his fault.</i></font>

58
00:07:07,770 --> 00:07:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara...</font>

59
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

60
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness...</font>

61
00:07:18,060 --> 00:07:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla.</font>

62
00:07:20,370 --> 00:07:22,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please don't, Prince Aqua!</i></font>

63
00:07:33,290 --> 00:07:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please, Prince Aqua...</i></font>

64
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:40,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Would you indulge my 
selfish whims once more?</i></font>

65
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

66
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

67
00:08:00,980 --> 00:08:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love Prince Aqua more than 
anyone in the world!</font>

68
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara?</font>

69
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How could I do something so ridiculous?</i></font>

70
00:08:19,730 --> 00:08:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

71
00:08:22,610 --> 00:08:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua?!</font>

72
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... Prince Aqua!</font>

73
00:08:34,290 --> 00:08:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara!</font>

74
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The sweet voice he always uses...</i></font>

75
00:08:44,260 --> 00:08:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe I let a drug overtake me.</font>

76
00:08:46,690 --> 00:08:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never forgive myself 
for being so spineless.</font>

77
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:55,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't spineless at all!</font>

78
00:08:56,220 --> 00:08:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

79
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's pitch-black.</font>

80
00:09:11,490 --> 00:09:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't realize it was this bad.</font>

81
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aquasteed.</font>

82
00:09:18,890 --> 00:09:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara.</font>

83
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're finally here.</font>

84
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiararose, I'm sorry Pearl's 
caused so much trouble.</font>

85
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also failed to be attentive enough.</font>

86
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Pearl isn't the only one to blame.</font>

87
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon you will feel 
the same pain that I feel.</font>

88
00:09:39,730 --> 00:09:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>King Pearl is hurting.</i></font>

89
00:09:41,990 --> 00:09:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if it's a misunderstanding, 
it's my fault.</i></font>

90
00:09:45,470 --> 00:09:47,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look like you're in pain. 
What happened?</font>

91
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're even wounded!</font>

92
00:09:50,140 --> 00:09:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That...</font>

93
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:54,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is all my fault.</font>

94
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I forced His Highness to drink 
the secret elixir of the sea.</font>

95
00:09:59,410 --> 00:10:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Secret elixir? You don't mean Pearl's...</font>

96
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That little...</font>

97
00:10:04,590 --> 00:10:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's so hopeless.</font>

98
00:10:06,610 --> 00:10:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The drug's effects shouldn't last long,</font>

99
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Pearl should have the antidote.</font>

100
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll go see her right away!</font>

101
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't.</font>

102
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This ocean is dangerous, even to us.</font>

103
00:10:18,730 --> 00:10:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If a human like you goes in, 
you'll never last.</font>

104
00:10:23,170 --> 00:10:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am prepared for that.</font>

105
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla, you mustn't!</font>

106
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

107
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to worry about me,</font>

108
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we can't leave 
the ocean in this state.</font>

109
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I realize that this is a problem</font>

110
00:10:38,010 --> 00:10:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that the humans and sea fairies 
should resolve together,</font>

111
00:10:43,290 --> 00:10:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but since we don't know how 
to return the ocean to normal,</font>

112
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're the only ones we can depend on.</font>

113
00:10:49,570 --> 00:10:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you please lend us your aid?</font>

114
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I beg you.</font>

115
00:10:57,930 --> 00:11:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm begging you, too!</font>

116
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want our beautiful ocean to come back!</font>

117
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, do you know 
why there are three fairy kings?</font>

118
00:11:11,190 --> 00:11:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I don't.</font>

119
00:11:12,850 --> 00:11:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that if one of us 
loses their way, suffers,</font>

120
00:11:16,660 --> 00:11:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and warps nature, 
the rest of us can right it.</font>

121
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be precise, humans blessed 
by the other two fairies must fix it.</font>

122
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that really true?</font>

123
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, Aquasteed, 
have received my blessing,</font>

124
00:11:32,310 --> 00:11:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Tiararose has received Keith's.</font>

125
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the two of you use your magic, 
you can restore the ocean.</font>

126
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

127
00:11:40,730 --> 00:11:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

128
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I can help heal this vast ocean?</font>

129
00:11:45,060 --> 00:11:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

130
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't have enough magic power!</font>

131
00:11:49,570 --> 00:11:53,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua does, 
but my magic is not enough!</font>

132
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have a choice.</font>

133
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

134
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My magic can heal this ocean?</i></font>

135
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:22,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do major events like this 
really happen to villainesses?</i></font>

136
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:28,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be fine. Can you trust me?</font>

137
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua...</font>

138
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aqua indulged my selfish request.</i></font>

139
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now it's my turn to believe in him.</i></font>

140
00:12:42,250 --> 00:12:43,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claire.</font>

141
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:48,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bestow the blessing of the Sky Fairy 
King upon Aquasteed Marinforest.</font>

142
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm putting my hopes in you,</font>

143
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and your strength 
as this nation's future king.</font>

144
00:12:56,340 --> 00:12:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Keith?</font>

145
00:12:58,930 --> 00:13:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bestow the blessing of the Forest Fairy 
King upon Tiararose Lapis Marinforest.</font>

146
00:13:04,490 --> 00:13:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm right here. You need only 
keep your eyes facing forward.</font>

147
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right, Tiara.</font>

148
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm right beside you.</font>

149
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:49,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my power we're talking about. 
There's no way you can fail.</font>

150
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:52,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua... Keith...</font>

151
00:13:53,250 --> 00:13:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel better now.</i></font>

152
00:13:56,020 --> 00:14:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, I can't even 
imagine these two losing.</i></font>

153
00:14:02,350 --> 00:14:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do this, Tiara.</font>

154
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:08,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll lend you my power. 
Call forth the trees and purify the ocean.</font>

155
00:14:08,300 --> 00:14:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

156
00:14:12,230 --> 00:14:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trees of the forest, lend me 
the power to protect this kingdom.</font>

157
00:14:22,910 --> 00:14:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing... This is the power 
of the Forest Fairy King?</font>

158
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blast it! Tiara's magic 
isn't strong enough!</font>

159
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it. Because I'm not the heroine...</i></font>

160
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

161
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think we could use these cookies?</font>

162
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have my magic in them.</font>

163
00:14:48,370 --> 00:14:49,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

164
00:14:52,220 --> 00:14:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it'll work.</font>

165
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:05,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can feel magic 
coursing through my body.</i></font>

166
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Trees of the forest, please!</i></font>

167
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These trees will absorb 
the contaminated water.</font>

168
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That just leaves...</font>

169
00:15:29,530 --> 00:15:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here with you, 
so you have to protect the ocean.</font>

170
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Aquasteed! 
Put more of your magic into it!</font>

171
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

172
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wind, bring light to this black ocean!</font>

173
00:16:29,630 --> 00:16:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's beautiful!</font>

174
00:16:31,070 --> 00:16:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did great.</font>

175
00:16:32,610 --> 00:16:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua, could it be...</font>

176
00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it seems the drug's 
effects have worn off.</font>

177
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your magic entered my body 
through the cookie I ate.</font>

178
00:16:43,250 --> 00:16:44,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That must be why.</font>

179
00:16:45,590 --> 00:16:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad!</font>

180
00:16:52,170 --> 00:16:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, I love you.</font>

181
00:16:54,410 --> 00:16:56,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for believing in me.</font>

182
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should be thanking you.</font>

183
00:17:00,540 --> 00:17:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad we were able to 
heal the ocean together.</font>

184
00:17:13,310 --> 00:17:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara?</font>

185
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's nothing.</font>

186
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Aqua is dripping 
with handsomeness!</i></font>

187
00:17:21,360 --> 00:17:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But this Prince Aqua is mine alone.</i></font>

188
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:26,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your hand is so warm, Tiara.</font>

189
00:17:26,860 --> 00:17:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for touching you 
with my wet hand!</font>

190
00:17:29,810 --> 00:17:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to do it more, actually.</font>

191
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should feel cold from the water, 
but somehow, I feel hot.</i></font>

192
00:17:40,850 --> 00:17:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My heart is pounding.</i></font>

193
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:46,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Did you two forget we're here?</font>

194
00:17:46,620 --> 00:17:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, now. They worked so hard. 
What's the problem?</font>

195
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're both soaked. I'll dry you off.</font>

196
00:17:57,420 --> 00:17:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It feels so warm and cozy.</i></font>

197
00:17:59,990 --> 00:18:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

198
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

199
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, look.</font>

200
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, what adorable flowers!</font>

201
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a new species 
that bloomed from your magic.</font>

202
00:18:18,060 --> 00:18:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My magic?</font>

203
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

204
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There seems to be something in it.</font>

205
00:18:23,980 --> 00:18:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

206
00:18:25,770 --> 00:18:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's your flower, 
so why don't you open it?</font>

207
00:18:29,170 --> 00:18:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

208
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a sweet scent.</i></font>

209
00:18:36,300 --> 00:18:38,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could this be...</i></font>

210
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara!</font>

211
00:18:41,390 --> 00:18:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's fine.</font>

212
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:47,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? It's very sweet, delicious sugar!</font>

213
00:18:50,370 --> 00:18:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know if I should say that's 
just what I'd expect from you or...</font>

214
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Prince Aqua?!</font>

215
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, your finger is sweet, all right.</font>

216
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough! Stop doing things 
that make me jealous!</font>

217
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara is my wife!</font>

218
00:19:12,210 --> 00:19:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, really, you two. 
Can't you just get along?</font>

219
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going?</font>

220
00:19:21,330 --> 00:19:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

221
00:19:26,330 --> 00:19:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claire's probably angrier 
about all this than anyone.</font>

222
00:19:31,940 --> 00:19:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike me, he actually likes humans.</font>

223
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he'll handle it 
just fine, though.</font>

224
00:19:39,650 --> 00:19:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's scary when he's mad, you know.</font>

225
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keith! This is no laughing matter!</font>

226
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, sure it is.</font>

227
00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can count on Claire to handle Pearl.</font>

228
00:19:54,060 --> 00:19:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We returned the ocean to normal,</i></font>

229
00:19:56,180 --> 00:19:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but Pearl's heart is still...</i></font>

230
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going, too.</font>

231
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:08,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There may be nothing I can do,</font>

232
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I want to talk 
to King Pearl one more time.</font>

233
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara...</font>

234
00:20:14,860 --> 00:20:17,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Pearl's castle is under the sea.</font>

235
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you going to see her?</font>

236
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

237
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't mind, 
could I come along as well?</font>

238
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla?</font>

239
00:20:29,040 --> 00:20:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm an absolute fool 
and a horrible person.</font>

240
00:20:33,130 --> 00:20:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have known I couldn't change</font>

241
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness's feelings 
with such a potion.</font>

242
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't ask you to forgive me.</font>

243
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you would grant me one chance,</font>

244
00:20:47,930 --> 00:20:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will protect Lady Tiararose 
with my very life.</font>

245
00:20:52,390 --> 00:20:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, please... please...</font>

246
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for offering.</font>

247
00:21:04,090 --> 00:21:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll feel much better if you're with us.</font>

248
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:13,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, are you sure about this?</font>

249
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. You can head back to the city.</font>

250
00:21:16,580 --> 00:21:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put the people at ease with the news 
that we've healed the ocean.</font>

251
00:21:21,510 --> 00:21:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara's starting to sound like 
a crown princess, isn't she?</font>

252
00:21:24,970 --> 00:21:27,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, she really is.</font>

253
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be going, then.</font>

254
00:21:35,450 --> 00:21:38,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure this wouldn't 
have happened at all</i></font>

255
00:21:38,660 --> 00:21:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>if I'd never come to this country.</i></font>

256
00:21:41,700 --> 00:21:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's why I have to 
see this through to the end.</i></font>

257
00:21:49,630 --> 00:21:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Including the future of those two...</i></font>

258
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the end of this game!</i></font>

259
