00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><b><font size="25"><font color="#3d8afc"><font color="#f76bb3"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Is <b><font color="#3d8afc">Always</font></b> <font color="#6b3e34">and <b><font color="#3d8afc">Forever</font></b></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font>

262
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><b><font size="25"><font color="#3d8afc"><font color="#f76bb3"><b>Love</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Is <b><font color="#3d8afc">Always</font></b> <font color="#6b3e34">and <b><font color="#3d8afc">Forever</font></b></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font>

263
00:23:31,140 --> 00:23:34,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, I will always be by your side.</font>

264
00:23:35,360 --> 00:23:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what the future holds, 
as long as I'm with you...</font>

